northstar

Tidy Healthcare Revenue Integrity


📦 Installation

You can install northstar from GitHub with:

# install.packages("pak")
pak::pak("andrewallenbruce/northstar")

🔰 Usage 

library(northstar)

Describe HCPCS 

describe_hcpcs(hcpcs = c("33924", "43116"))
